19. TYPES OF MACHINE LEARNING

A. Supervised Learning
- Uses labeled data
- Learns mapping from inputs to known outputs

Examples:
- Classification
- Regression

B. Unsupervised Learning
- Uses unlabeled data
- Finds hidden patterns or structure

Examples:
- Clustering
- Dimensionality reduction

C. Reinforcement Learning
