Deployment means making the trained model available for real use.

Examples:
- Web app prediction service
- Fraud detection API
- Recommendation engine in production
- Real-time classification endpoint

Deployment turns experimentation into practical value.

--------------------------------------------------
34. MONITORING

After deployment, models must be monitored.

Why:
- Performance can degrade over time
- Real-world data can change
- User behavior can shift
- Data quality may drop

Monitoring helps ensure the model remains useful and reliable.

